data.text:
Join us for a Memorial Day's Eve hammer jammer at Greensburg's nerve center for DIY ventures featuring:

Halo Bite (blistering hxc from NY)

https://halobite.bandcamp.com

Princess (pgh hardcore punk)

https://princesshc.bandcamp.com

Bala Rise & the Uprising (thrash hxc from pgh)

https://uprisinghxc.bandcamp.com/

...By the Deed (pgh hxc)

https://www.instagram.com/bythedeed412/

Abstentious (Altoona punk)

https://www.instagram.com/ab_stentious

Sunday May 26, 2024 @ Green Beacon Gallery

235 W. Pittsburgh St. Greensburg, PA 15601

Doors 7:30 // Show 8pm

All ages // BYOB 21+ with valid ID

$13 cover

Free parking on street and in large lot in gallery rear. Please enter through front door. All gallery artwork available to browse and buy during the show, features 500+ works from over 200 local/regional artists & makers!
